 Description:   <Neuricam PCCam image viewer>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------


pccam_viewer is a simple application that allows the user to grab and display
images under the XWindow system. In order to recompile the source code 
the following tools/libraries are nedeed:

1 - gtk+2 
2 - atk-1.0
3 - pango-1.0 

These packages are already installed on the PCCam operating system.
Compile the source code using the command described in the pccam_viewer.c
header.
